Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:05.73,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}不再被自身限界束縛 為你解放自我極限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.61,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Nobody Knows 未來的事誰都無能知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.49,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}一切的信任都可能石沉大海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.70,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}放眼望去一切都是未知數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:20.67,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Nobody　Ends 不要再依賴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:25.17,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}重要的秘密無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.47,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}都會惹是招非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:32.55,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}這樣下去的話 只會止步於此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:38.02,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}伸出手和你十指緊扣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.73,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}只是逞強的話誰都無法保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.15,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}這份思念猶如湛藍之色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:48.11,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}在不經意間 扣下愛的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:52.61,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}現在用只屬於我們的海誓山盟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.78,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}將一切阻礙擊碎
